Steps to Solve:

-Discover the hidden /admin endpoint.
-Browse to:
/admin
-Notice that only DontWannaCry users can access the admin panel.
-Open the Email Client and copy your unique email domain:
@YOUR-EMAIL-ID.web-security-academy.net
-Register a new account using a very long email address:
very-long-string@YOUR-EMAIL-ID.web-security-academy.net
-Make sure the local part is longer than 200 characters.
-Confirm the account from the Email Client.
-Log in and check the My account page.
-Notice that the email address is truncated to:
255 characters
-Log out and register another account using this format:
very-long-string@dontwannacry.com.YOUR-EMAIL-ID.web-security-academy.net
-Adjust the length so the m in:
@dontwannacry.com

is exactly character 255.

-Confirm the new account through the Email Client.
-Log in with the new account.
-Access the admin panel:
/admin
-Delete the user carlos.
-The lab is solved.
